\" target=\"_blank\">http://booking.com</a> <br />\n個 account 睇到我個訂單，搞到我以為訂錯咗。<br />\n<br />\n酒店都話冇我 agoda 張單，話係 <a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=11fb81b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://booking.com</a>  就有。<br />\n<br />\n搞到我同酒店覆咗幾日 email.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地唔同集團，不過之間有合約，<a href=\"http://所以係agoda訂完有機會會彈去booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E4%BF%82agoda%E8%A8%82%E5%AE%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E5%BD%88%E5%8E%BBbooking.com&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=58335f28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">所以係agoda訂完有機會會彈去booking.com</a> (相反就唔會)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係咁簡單，係就唔會我用兩邊 account 都查到同一間酒店有訂單，搞到我以為訂重覆咗，以為 <a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=11fb81b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">booking.com</a> 撳錯制訂咗，用 <a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=11fb81b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">booking.com</a> account 取消，佢叫我直接搵酒店，同酒店話 cancel ，佢覆我話條款冇得退錢喎。<br />\n<br />\n再問多兩問，酒店話冇收到我 agoda 張單，最後先知原來係同一個 booking."},{"pid":"6275c15b8ce4878c1103ab7a548c221a56c39b5e","tid":136794,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T12:17:45.000Z","msg":"依家多數用 <a href=\"http://hotel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotel.com&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=68873850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hotel.com</a> ,貪佢有十送一，一年一定回饋到一次。<br />\n<br />\n不過如果間酒店佢冇做就搵 <a href=\"http://booking.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbooking.com&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&